data.text: @BraveLittleDrk1 Dms love.
~ {I slide closer to @BraveLittleDrk1 staring at the smooth concrete cemetery floor below.}
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ me of my humanity. What's left of it. Your hands the blood. Are yiu getting out of control with your feeding love? ~
{I move my hand squeezing yours tight caressing it down your jawline back to your cheek.} I enjoy it myself it reminds ~ @BraveLittleDrk1
@_Wild_Angel I am glad you enjoyed it, Cheri.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ gently closes my eyes nodding deep brows.}
I enjoy it very much so. I don't get to enjoy it much. But yes I do. {Nods moving my fingers soft over the top of @BraveLittleDrk1 hand~
{squeezes @BraveLittleDrk1 hand tight nods with a smirk.} The things the night holds. The people. The places. The divine tastes.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ Do not feel lost Cheri. I am here. And their are so many more out there as well. Just not all you can trust love. ~
So kind of you, Cheri. {grins wide feeling your lips touching my hand squeezing it tight.} Indeed, love. I will not~  @BraveLittleDrk1
https://t.co/Ast8ysKgSN Hoping, hating, things that I can't bare...
https://t.co/Ast8ysKgSN @_Wild_Angel Music for you, Cheri.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ away with deepened brows nods.} Such sadness can be in the night as well.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ so pleasing. I have had my nights. Something that has torn away at me through the centuries ofcourse. {gazes ~
{I straight my frock on my coat nodding at @BraveLittleDrk1 chuckling.} I enjoy your spirit love. Unfortunately it hasn't always been~
Such things I could show you? I am going to give you the choice. I never had.
@_Wild_Angel Causing trouble. Being indefinitely evil. Naughty. Ravishing the night. And you?
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ Living in the darkness is quite fun. The night holds such beauty. I enjoy it very much so.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ killed his self soon after into the fire. But that's another story. I learned mostly on my own, Cheri. And yes ~
{I turn a slight grin playing on my lips nods} I am old enough turned in the late 1700's ofcourse. My maker unfortunately~ @BraveLittleDrk1
@_Wild_Angel Indeed. {wiggles brows licks fangs}
@_Wild_Angel I am well Cheri. Enjoying the pleasures of this beautiful night.
@Radiant_Sookie {chuckles} Both at times. I can be evil. But its in my nature ofcourse.
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ patting a spot next to me on the floor next to my coffin.}
Never doubt your english, Cheri. Over the centuries. I have perfected it being a frenchmen ofcourse. {chuckles ~ @BraveLittleDrk1
{Pokes @_Wild_Angel back.} Bonjour Cheri. How are you?
{chuckles again nodding.} Cheri...I can be a bit of a perfect devil. @Radiant_Sookie
@BraveLittleDrk1 ~ I do enjoy Louisiana. Reminds me of my home in France. {smiles walking inside taking a seat next to my coffin.}
Live here? This is where I am at the moment. I stay in the darkness roaming. ~ @BraveLittleDrk1
~ this would not be difficult for vampire prince. But I am a bit difficult to deal with. Louis said you are a devil Lestat. @Radiant_Sookie
{chuckles nodding arching a brow.} Perhaps you are right, Cheri. You would think after so many centuries~ @Radiant_Sookie
~ How are you love? Won't you come in? @BraveLittleDrk1
{I blur to the door grasping the knob twisting it open creaking slowly arches a brow fanged grin} Bonjour, Cheri. ~ @BraveLittleDrk1
~ try the same. Maybe my beloveds will return to me one day. Or night ofcourse. {chuckles.} @Radiant_Sookie
{nods grins slightly with a sigh.} Indeed. Seems for a lonely vampire myself wondering the world alone. Perhaps I should~ @Radiant_Sookie
@Radiant_Sookie ~ the stars.} Yes simply amazing.
I am un-sure unfortunately.  Jess. Or my dearest, Louis. Such a shame. {nods blurring over sitting with @Radiant_Sookie staring up at ~
@Radiant_Sookie ~ as well. Such an amazing night. Don't you agree?
{grins nodding.} What bear love? And it has been ages since I last saw you? I haven't seen my dearest beloved in ages ~ @Radiant_Sookie
@Radiant_Sookie ~ seen my you in what seems like ages. I am glad things are well for you love.
{nods tilting my head with a softer smile to ease the tension at @Radiant_Sookie.} Your, beloved? That's simply amazing. I haven't ~
{grins fangs extended nodding.} Thats good love? And what makes you so happy this dark night, cheri? I am well. @Radiant_Sookie
@Radiant_Sookie Bonjour, cheri. Madame, Sookie. {Fanged grin arching a slight brow.} How are you this morning?
Bonjour mes enfants de la nuit.[grins devilishly.] Such a beautiful night. You are all so beautiful.
https://t.co/8BOx59fxXM Sorry. I'm late was catching my breakfast.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --in a blur into the night.]
--[I bow taking @BraveLittleDrk1's hand placing a cold kiss.] Until tomorrow beautiful child of darkness. [I release your hand vanishing--
Indeed. I look foward to seeing you again, Cheri. Goodnight. And may flights of angels bring you to your rest. -- @BraveLittleDrk1
I shall be leaving soon. I must take to my coffin. Before dawns early light. Bonne nuit mes enfants de la nuit! [Fanged grin.]
@BraveLittleDrk1 --fanged grin.] We can meet again tomorrow at night fall if you wish?
You're more than welcome, Cheri. Stop by anytime. You will know when you arrive where to find me ofcourse. [I nod at @BraveLittleDrk1 sly--
Now, now, Cheri. No need for that. I simply asked you a question. What is your reasoning? @BratPrincess123
@BraveLittleDrk1 --mostly likely be staying in the french quarters. You may visit. Just on the other side of the cemetery.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --I will take that under consideration cheri. I do love company. I have just arrived again in New Orleans. I will--
[I vanish in a moments blur taking a seat on some steps a few feet away gazing up at @BraveLittleDrk1. I turn a sly grin.] --
"We are predators, Whose all seeing eyes were meant to give them detachment."
Hm. I don't normally share my blood. May I ask your reasoning? [I arch a brow curiously at @BratPrincess123.]
@BraveLittleDrk1 --your precious gift. Experience is the best teacher of all. That is my first bit of advice.
--[I chuckle lightly at @BraveLittleDrk1's excitement in amusement.] Louis will come around. They always do. Merciful death how you love--
@BraveLittleDrk1 --his death soon after making me born of darkness. I am here for you my child of darkness. Whenever you need. --
@BraveLittleDrk1 --make the one who made you very proud. And lucky as well. I on the other hand learned mostly on my own. My maker met--
[I tilt my head again wide fanged grin spreading across my feautures nodding at @BraveLittleDrk1.] You are very wise young one. You must--
[I tilt my head arching a brow at @BratPrincess123.] Ask away, Cheri? Perhaps I can asist?
@BraveLittleDrk1 --immortality is a gift. One he hasn't learned to except.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --not happy with his dark gift. Most of the time. But, I do love my dear sweet Louis. I haven't seen him much.--
[I shake my head at @BraveLittleDrk1 with a low sigh.] Unfortunately he doesn't listen to any of my advice most of the time. He is--
Typos already very disappointed. These human contraptions are quite annoying.
You are a fan? I try to remain in the darkness anymore. A pleasure to meet you love. [I nod taking @BratPrincess123 hand bowing.]
@BraveLittleDrk1 --view.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --shall we. And none so creatures are like God but, ourselves. I know that evil exist. Its just a beautiful point of--
@BraveLittleDrk1 --And evil is as well. Is a point of view. Something. I told Louis many years ago. God kills indiscriminatly. And so--
[I grin tilting my head fanged grin arching a slight brow at @BraveLittleDrk1.] An artist? I am an artist of music. And the dark.--
--Tell me how bad I am. It makes me feel so good!"
"I don't think anyone will ever say it quite like you do. Come on, say it again. I'm a perfect devil.--
@BratPrincess123 Ah you have returned, Cheri. I am quite well ofcourse love. And how are you? [I tilt my head arching a brow.]
@BraveLittleDrk1 --my tongue over a fang winks.]
@BraveLittleDrk1 --evils that exist. Like old sweet wine. The crimsom that fulfills my thirst. [I lean closer widening my grin running --
@BraveLittleDrk1 --always put it "Lestat you're a perfect devil. Hm. I only thrive. And take what the night has to offer such glorious--
There is such things. The night is full of beauty. Such things I do so thrive upon being a perfect devil. As Louis -- @BraveLittleDrk1
@BraveLittleDrk1 --think. I am a devil in the night. Beautiful...I like that. And agree its in our nature to feed as we will.
[I move swiftly to @BraveLittleDrk1 side with a quick movement in a blink lowering my hands to my side.] Beautiful you say? Hm. Most --
Nice to meet you, Cheri. [Nods taking @ravynagain hand with a bow fanged grin.] Such a pleasure indeed.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --such a shame. I will never understand wanting to co-exist with humans. Nor shall I. I live by my own law.
[I nod straightening my leather coat fanged grin on my feautures gazing up at the night sky.] The old way is better-- @BraveLittleDrk1
My apologies if my replies are slow. I am getting my notifications slowly for some reason. Humans and their devices. [Smirks.]
Indeed. [Fanged grin.] @ravynagain: *dies* because I just found out that  @theLestat is on twitter o_O
--in a blur standing next to @BraveLittleDrk1 straighting my sleeve of my shirt with a grin.] Such a shame to live by rules.
@BraveLittleDrk1 --nowadays.  No fun. I prefer the old way ofcourse. Feeding in the night. Traveling the earth. In the shadows.[I appear--
[Nods with a sly grin at @BraveLittleDrk1] Indeed. Authority buisiness?  I have no authority.  I live by my own law. These Vampires -
@SookieTBFae Good to see you as well Madame, Sookie. -Nods fanged grin.-
@BraveLittleDrk1 --night indeed. And no the pleasure is all mine. Walking alone in the shadows for so long. I enjoy the company, Cheri.
-I place a small kiss on @BraveLittleDrk1 hand releasing. I step back leaning against a old statue with a fanged grin.-Such a dark cold--
https://t.co/Ast8ysKgSN "I see hell in your eyes! Taken in by surprise.Touching you makes me feel alive! Touching you makes me die inside!"
@BraveLittleDrk1 --placing my cool lips to the top.-
@BraveLittleDrk1 Is that so? Well its a pleasure to meet you Cass. I haven't been around much. I was away in Paris.-Bows taking your hand--
@BraveLittleDrk1 I am indeed, Cheri. The one. And only Vampire Lestat. -Bows with a fanged grin.- And you are love?
Such a quite night.  The mid of my morning. -Bows with a fanged grin.- Sorry I am late. I was trying to catch my breakfast.
@Jessie_Reeves_ Bon Matin, Jess. -Nods fanged grin.-
@AlixCattrall You are most welcome, Cheri.
@BraveLittleDrk1 You are most welcome, Cheri. -Bows fanged grin.-

This is work that requires constant attention and care, self-reflection and compassion. We are grateful to be on our own journey of integrating the 94 Calls to Action in our work, and learning how to be in better relationship ...

Restorative Justice Victoria exists in this context, and it feels imperative to reflect on how we can create a present without harm, a future where harm caused is acknowledged and addressed, and to work to build a relationship that can be harmonious and just.

... the countless deaths of children continues to happen? The term ‘reconciliation’ is about restoring harmony to a relationship, but what does that word mean when applied to a relationship that has never been harmonious and instead built on generations of genocide?

Our work aims to restore relationships after harm has happened, but it feels important to reflect on what this means in the context of the ongoing legacy of colonialism. What does reconciliation mean when harm in the form of violence, cultural erasure, and the unearthing of ...

We at Restorative Justice Victoria are in deep reflection and observance of the National Day for Truth and Reconciliation happening tomorrow, September 30, which is a day to honour those who survived and did not survive Canada’s horrible legacy of residential schools.
